Title: [ANN][CMT]CyberMiles-Incorporate blockchain tech. into the real e-commerce world
Body: The CMT Cube is a home-based device specifically designed to facilitate validator election during the first year of CyberMiles network operation. It is a hardware device that acts both a CMT wallet (stores and manages a CMT account), and an easy-to-use user interface, or UI, for staking the CMTs in the wallet to elect validators. Its UI also displays the up-to-date earnings (delegator‚Äôs block award) the account receives over time. The hardware wallet at home is much safer than web-based or phone-based software wallets, and hence is ideal for holding and staking significant amounts of CMTs. https://www.cybermiles.io/validator/

The CyberMiles blockchain platform will be fully compatible with Ethereum and the upcoming Cosmos network‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääso that application developers can freely move code and even crypto assets across blockchains. This decision was taken to safeguard a successful Token Sale and minimize regulatory risk, so that we can continue with our mission to Decentralize and Democratize E-Commerce with our blockchain applications.  The US will continue to be an important part of CyberMiles‚Äôs blockchain development, and 5miles will continue to be a strategic partner to bring our blockchain innovations to its millions of users. We look forward to having you remain a part of our CyberMiles community, but once again, we regret to inform you that we are not allowing US participation in the Token Sale.  Thanks for your understanding and on-going support.

Author: ululamri
Title: [ANN][CMT]CyberMiles-Incorporate blockchain tech. into the real e-commerce world
Body: In this scenario, the initial CMT based on ERC-20 will be exchanged on a 1:1 basis with the original CMT issued on blockchain CyberMiles, with stored values and rights transferred to the original token. all the CMT based on ERC-20 will burned after cybermiles blockchain launch  There are two uses of CMT: to reward community members for the services they provide, and to facilitate financial transactions on the network.
